Say '''Burauen''' et unaan ya klase baley ed luyag na [[Leyte]], [[Pilipinas]]. Unong ed 2010 Census, say papulasyon to et 48,853 totoo. Walay kabaleg tan sukat to ya 265.33 sq. km. Sikato et walad kumadwa ya distrito. Say zip code to et 6516.	
															
